<%
require 'date'
workday = { "name" => "Work Day",  "description" => "No upcoming workday", "start_time" => nil}
begin
    events = resource["events"].select { |e|
    	e["name"].downcase.include? "work" 
    }.sort_by { |start_time| }
    workday = events[0] if events[0] != nil

rescue Exception => e  
    workday = { :id => 0, :name => "No upcoming workdays",  :description => e}
end
%>

<div class="span3 sidebar" id="subnav">
	<ul class="nav nav-list sidenav">
		<li class="active"><a href="#information"><i class="icon-chevron-right"></i> Information</a></li>
		<li><a href="#easyfundraising"><i class="icon-chevron-right"></i> Easyfundraising</a></li>
		<li><a href="#calendar"><i class="icon-chevron-right"></i> Calendar</a></li>
	</ul>
</div>

<div class="span9">
	<section id="history">
		<div class="page-header">
		 	<h2>Information</h2>
	 	</div> 
		<div class="row-fluid">
			<div class="span4">
				<h2>Friends</h2>
				<p>The fund-raising team, are always looking for new ideas, but more importantly people who can help carry them out!! If you want to join us, <a class="sendmail" href="http://cprobert.wufoo.com/forms/nanyycwm/">get in touch with V</a> at the office.</p>
				<p><a class="btn" data-original-title="What we have achieved" href="#" id="acheived2011" title="">Achievements &raquo;</a></p>
			</div>

			<div class="span4">
				<h2>Newsletter</h2>
				<p>Please sign up for an electronic version of this Newsletter. &nbsp;Please send submissions to the school - Business ads cost &pound;2.50 per submission and should be paid at the school office or sent via cheque to Victoria Robinson, Ysgol Nant-y-Cwm, Llanycefn, Clynderwen, Pembrokeshire, SA66 7QJ. &nbsp;Thank you.</p>
				<p><a class="btn sendmail" href="http://bit.ly/nant-y-cwm" target="_blank">Subscribe &raquo;</a></p>
			</div>

			<div class="span4">
				<h2>Work Days</h2>
				<p>Info on work days here</p>

				<% if workday["start_time"] != nil %>
					<p><em>Next work day</em>: <%= Date.parse(workday["start_time"]).strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %></p>
					<p><%= workday["description"] %></p>
				<% end %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="easyfundraising">
  		<div class="page-header">
			<h2>Easyfundraising</h2>
		</div>
		
		<p>We have registered with easyfundraising.  It is a website from which you click through to the on-line retailer. The retailer then donates a percentage cost of the order (at no extra cost to the shopper.) Donations range from 0.5% to 20% of the purchase price or some categories give specific cash values.</p>

		<div class="alert alert-success">
			<h4>It is free to use</h4>
			 It's a really easy way to raise funds for the school.  Money raised is paid quarterly. Friends, neighbours and family might want to register too- spread the word! There are over 2000 retailers - see if the one you want is there, click through and raise some money for the school!
		</div>

		<p><a class="btn btn-large btn-success" href="http://www.easyfundraising.org.uk/causes/friendsofnantycwm" target="_blank">Cool Sign-me-up</a></p>
	</section>	

	<section id="calendar">
  		<div class="page-header">
			<h2>Calendar</h2>
		</div>

		<table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-hover table-condensed">
		      <thead>
		        <tr class="info">
		          <th>Event</th>
		          <th>Date</th>
		          <th>Details</th>
		        </tr>
		      </thead>
		      <tbody>
		        <% 
		        require 'date'
		        begin
		            resource["events"].each do |event| 
		            %>
		            <tr>
		              <td><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/<%=event["id"] %>/" target="fb"><%=event["name"] %></a></td>
		              <td><%= Date.parse(event["start_time"]).strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %></td>
		              <td><%= ScmsUtils.txt_2_html(event["description"]) %></td>
		            </tr>
		            <% 
		            end
		        rescue
		            puts "No events"
		        end
		        %>
		      </tbody>
		 </table>
	</section>
</div>

